1
00:00:00,698 --> 00:00:06,820
When my husband was going into the dining room this morning,
今天早晨我丈夫走进饭厅时,

2
00:00:06,943 --> 00:00:10,941
he dropped some coins on the floor.
他把一些硬币掉在地上了.

3
00:00:10,984 --> 00:00:14,408
There were coins everywhere.
到处都是硬币.

4
00:00:14,689 --> 00:00:19,662
We looked for them, but we could not find them all.
我们找了,但没有把它们全部找到.

5
00:00:19,663 --> 00:00:22,864
While we were having breakfast, 
正当我们吃早饭时,

6
00:00:23,105 --> 00:00:30,526
our little boy, Tommy, found two small coins on the floor.
我们的小男孩Tommy在地上找到了两枚小硬币.

7
00:00:30,527 --> 00:00:34,487
He put them both into his mouth.
他把那两枚硬币都放进了嘴里.

8
00:00:34,725 --> 00:00:40,754
We both tried to get the coins, but it was too late.
我们俩都试图把这两枚硬币拿出来,但太迟了.

9
00:00:41,276 --> 00:00:46,383
Tommy had already swallowed them!
汤米已经把硬币咽了下去!

10
00:00:46,654 --> 00:00:52,344
Later that morning, when I was doing the housework, 
那天下午的晚些时候,当我正做家务时,

11
00:00:52,995 --> 00:00:57,538
My husband phoned me from the office.
我丈夫从办公室打来电话.

12
00:00:57,622 --> 00:01:01,005
How's Tommy?' he asked.
“汤米怎么样?”他问.

13
00:01:01,151 --> 00:01:04,610
I don't know,' I answered,
“我不知道”,我回答说,

14
00:01:04,633 --> 00:01:10,314
Tommy's been to the toilet three times this morning,
“今天上午汤米去了3次厕所了,

15
00:01:10,477 --> 00:01:14,374
but I haven't had any change yet!'
但我还没看到硬币!”

